      "widgets_values": [
        "Tim: Hello. [break=0.4] Are you the new software engineer?\nLogan: Oh, hi! [break=0.3] Yes, that's right. I'm, uh, new here. My name is Logan.\nTim: I'm Tim. [break=0.3] I work as a sales manager. Nice to meet you.\nLogan: Nice to meet you too. [break=0.6] Excuse me — I actually have a quick question. Who's responsible for developing the Bit app? [break=0.4] The app is great, and the code is really clean.\nTim: Ah, [break=0.2] that's Kawashima. [break=0.4] He's the head of the dev team — he's responsible for all of the applications.\nLogan: I'd love to ask him some questions about the app's features. [break=0.3] Can I meet him?\nTim: Hmm, [break=0.3] he's not here. [break=0.5] He works at our headquarters, in Japan. [break=0.4] I'll text you his number and email. [break=0.3] But honestly, [break=0.2] I don't think he'll answer your call — he's very busy.\nLogan: I'll email him then. [break=0.3] Thank you so much!",
        "1.7B",
